Module fi.tuni.prog3.sisufxml
Package fi.tuni.prog3.sisufxml

Class ModuleEntry

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.prog3.sisufxml.ModuleEntry
public class ModuleEntry extends Object
A class for representing a module in the study structure. Several types of modules are supported. Contains all relevant information about an individual module. If module is not a course, can contain child modules.
Author:
Arttu
